{"tid":2098950,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"世界上分咗2種人：追求者同被追求者","createTime":"2020-07-08T01:05:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T05:57:06.000Z","uid":258246,"like":12,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d4cd3327fbb31962df3cf1cb816af880a6dee3b5","tid":2098950,"uid":258246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T01:05:04.000Z","msg":"世界上分咗2種人：<br />\n追求者同被追求者。<br />\n<br />\n大家鍾意做邊類人多啲！<br />\n<br />\n正評：追人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n負評：被人追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：<br />\n女。做慣追人同埋製造機會嗰個。<br />\n表示鍾意自己有得帶節奏，<br />\nsense到對方唔受溝就可以轉下一個。<br />\nsense到對方受，<br />\n就可以睇時機加重本錢。<br />\n就算第一次表白俾人reject咗，<br />\n都可以扮自己其實講下笑，<br />\n然後繼續同對方做好朋友。<br />\n等人地覺得「死啦原來我真係鍾意佢」，<br />\n就可以順理成章等人表白。<br />\n<br />\n完全唔理解鍾意俾人追嗰啲咩心態。<br />\n係咪真係咁自卑，<br />\n要靠俾人追求嘅過程去獲取對自己嘅認同感 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe890098e49941952e6570f123713665471b8af8","tid":2098950,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T01:05:50.000Z","msg":"追我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d88481d934f60091d8f27e5c621e7ac596d3221e","tid":2098950,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T01:06:26.000Z","msg":"人善被人J"},{"pid":"78fe609cf7e823e0958a30078e75a428c86280f1","tid":2098950,"uid":231957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T01:09:43.000Z","msg":"同埋  毒撚阿 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e6fd87849dba07eb29749ccc3756a4c828df8ea","tid":2098950,"uid":199670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T01:10:35.000Z","msg":"女咪可以咁做 男就<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28da6